snippet.title: Flutter Beta & the Hamilton App - DevShow at DartConf 2018
snippet.description:
Tim Sneath (Group Product Manager of Flutter & Dart) discusses Flutter Beta and the Hamilton App, developed with Flutter, at Dart Conf 2018. Watch this episode of The Developer Show to learn how Flutter inspired Tim to join Google and why he thinks 2018 is the year of Flutter.

Watch the Keynote with Tim Sneath → https://goo.gl/QuRh3h
Catch all the sessions from DartConf 2018 here → https://goo.gl/WqfKf2
Check out DevShow’s event coverage → https://goo.gl/R1htuu
